settings.description: Wendy gets her Airship redesigned, With various Airships added for assistant, Mario goes to the airship by using an mini airship instead of climbing, Good Luck Defeating Wendy & Finding a Secret Exit

A remake of Super Mario World 1-1. Somehow, Rexes are now red and hopping. Banzai Bills are now smaller and homes in to you.
[Revision 2: Backtracking from room 2 disabled due to graphical glitches]
Embarking a Journey on the First Unused level but It's Improved by a little bit, Good luck finding the hidden Ace coins!

First level! This is the first of what will be a 72 (plus 1 extra for those who complete all 72 levels 100%!) level series! This will take a while! Good luck getting all 360 Ace coins!
Difficulty: 3/5

I'm sure every level set needs an underwater stage! And where there is water, there is bound to be a frog somewhere in it!
Difficulty: 4/5

A representation of the 8 worlds! This level contains worlds 5-8!
Difficulty: 5/5

A representation of the 8 worlds! This level contains worlds 1-4!
Difficulty: 3/5

Just keep running, and don't stop! Let the triangular blocks guide you!
Difficulty: 2/5
Dodge the bullets, Touch the snake Corners, and defeat Lemmy, He has more lives and resistance to fire than ever before. Good luck defeating Lemmy and finding the secret exit!

Mario traverses through the 4 elements of Water, Earth, Fire, and Air! Water room is a bit buggy!
Difficulty: 2/5

True to my title's namesake, this is a fire and ice level! Be careful, this one's tough!
Difficulty: 5/5
